# Normalize all text to LF in the repo and on checkout. This project is edited
# on Windows but deployed to a Linux droplet — CRLF in shell scripts (e.g.
# deploy/setup.sh) breaks on the droplet, so keep everything LF.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gz binary
*.tgz binary
*.sqlite binary
